# Course Content Hierarchy

EWA courses are organized in a strict four-level hierarchy. Always navigate top-down.

```
Section  (раздел — e.g. "Survival English")
  └── Unit  (юнит — e.g. "Greetings")
        └── Lesson  (урок — e.g. "Hello & Goodbye")
              └── Exercise  (упражнение — e.g. speechExercise "Say hello")
```

Grammar topics exist outside this hierarchy as a separate entity.

## Entity relationships

- `Unit.sectionId` → `Section._id`
- `Lesson.unitId` → `Unit._id`
- `Exercise.lessonId` → `Lesson._id`

## Section

Top-level grouping by theme and difficulty.

| Field             | Type        | Description                              |
|-------------------|-------------|------------------------------------------|
| `_id`             | string      | UUID                                     |
| `title`           | object      | Multilingual: `{ "en": "...", "ru": "..." }` |
| `description`     | object      | Multilingual description                 |
| `goalDescription` | object      | Multilingual learning goal               |
| `learningLanguage`| string      | ISO code: `en`, `es`, `de`, etc.         |
| `languageLevel`   | string      | `initial`, `beginner`, `elementary`, etc.|
| `number`          | int         | Sort order within the course             |
| `tags`            | string[]    | e.g. `["classic"]`                       |
| `isReady`         | object      | Per-language readiness: `{ "en": true }` |
| `isDeleted`       | bool        | Soft-delete flag                         |
| `translationProgress` | int    | Percentage of translations completed     |

## Unit

Groups lessons within a section.

| Field             | Type        | Description                              |
|-------------------|-------------|------------------------------------------|
| `_id`             | string      | UUID                                     |
| `sectionId`       | string      | Parent section UUID                      |
| `title`           | object      | Multilingual title                       |
| `learningLanguage`| string      | ISO code                                 |
| `number`          | int         | Sort order within section                |
| `tags`            | string[]    | Tags                                     |
| `isReady`         | object      | Per-language readiness                   |
| `isDeleted`       | bool        | Soft-delete flag                         |
| `translationProgress` | int    | Translation percentage                   |

## Lesson

Individual learning unit with exercises.

| Field          | Type        | Description                                    |
|----------------|-------------|------------------------------------------------|
| `_id`          | string      | UUID                                           |
| `unitId`       | string      | Parent unit UUID                               |
| `title`        | object      | Multilingual title                             |
| `kind`         | string      | Lesson type (see below)                        |
| `cefrLevel`    | string      | CEFR: `Pre-A1`, `A1`, `A2`, `B1`, `B2`, `C1`  |
| `cefrRange`    | string      | GSE range: `"22-29"`, `"43-58"`, etc.          |
| `difficulty`   | string/int  | `easy`, `medium`, `hard`                       |
| `status`       | string      | `draft`, `active`, `processing`, `history`     |
| `topic`        | string      | e.g. `restaurant`, `airport_dog_check`, `food` |
| `tags`         | string[]    | e.g. `["ai-generated", "grammar"]`             |
| `isReady`      | object      | Per-language readiness                         |
| `isDeleted`    | bool        | Soft-delete flag                               |
| `unitNumber`   | int         | Number within unit                             |
| `passScore`    | int         | Minimum score to pass                          |

### Lesson kinds

| Kind                | Description                          |
|---------------------|--------------------------------------|
| `common`            | Standard mixed exercises             |
| `words`             | Vocabulary-focused                   |
| `texts`             | Reading comprehension                |
| `dialogues`         | Pre-scripted dialogue practice       |
| `aiDialogue`        | AI-generated dialogue                |
| `chatTests`         | Chat-based assessment                |
| `vocabularyTests`   | Vocabulary quiz                      |
| `languageLevelTests`| Placement / level test               |
| `repeat`            | Review / spaced repetition           |

## Exercise

Atomic learning activity inside a lesson.

| Field         | Type        | Description                                 |
|---------------|-------------|---------------------------------------------|
| `_id`         | string      | UUID                                        |
| `lessonId`    | string      | Parent lesson UUID                          |
| `type`        | string      | Exercise type (see below)                   |
| `number`      | int         | Order within lesson (starts at 1)           |
| `content`     | object      | Multilingual content: `{ "ru": { "hint": "...", "text": "..." } }` |
| `word`        | string      | Word UUID reference (if vocabulary)         |
| `isValid`     | object      | Per-language validation: `{ "ru": true }`   |
| `isDeleted`   | bool        | Soft-delete flag                            |
| `isRepeatable`| bool        | Can be repeated                             |
| `isTesting`   | bool        | Included in test lesson                     |
| `sample`      | string      | Audio sample UUID                           |
| `videoUrl`    | string      | Resolved video URL                          |
| `llmMetadata` | object      | AI generation metadata                      |

Common exercise types: `speechExercise`, `composeWord`, `choosePicture`, `chooseTranslate`, `listenChoose`, `composePhrase`, `matchWords`, `fillGap`.

## Grammar

Standalone entity, not part of the section hierarchy. Linked to CEFR levels.

| Field          | Type        | Description                              |
|----------------|-------------|------------------------------------------|
| `_id`          | string      | Code-based ID: `A1_G1`, `B2_G3`         |
| `code`         | string      | Same as `_id`                            |
| `name`         | string      | Topic name: `"BE-sentences"`             |
| `cefr`         | string      | CEFR level: `A1`–`C2`                   |
| `gseMin`       | int         | GSE range start (0–100)                  |
| `gseMax`       | int         | GSE range end (0–100)                    |
| `description`  | string      | What the topic covers                    |
| `grammarRules` | string[]    | Rule identifiers                         |
| `isActive`     | bool        | Active flag                              |
| `order`        | int         | Sort order                               |
| `tags`         | string[]    | e.g. `["a1", "a1_g1"]`                  |
